                <div class="intro-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="intro-content last">
                    <h5><strong>Lots of features</strong></h5>
                    <p>{{ config('app.name') }} offers many features such as categorised transactions, tags, reports, recurring transactions, piggy banks and much more.</p>
